content: The dogs gonads

Has lots of potential. Includes mechanics like penetration values, angling, and different ammunition types from wot blitz. However I experienced plenty of glitches which caused my screen to jerk around and made it impossible to aim and play. If the performance issues were ironed out, I'm sure the game will be much more popular. If your device is able to handle this game then just go for it! Five stars for the effort. Suggestions: Perhaps you could release a free version that only has multiplayer to boost your popularity and low player base. With the price of the app, many would be hesitant to try it unless personally recommend by friends. A free multiplayer version will allow them to try the game before committing and let them  play with their friends.  The game also faces heavy competition from other popular tank games as well (like wot blitz). I really hope that the gameplay can be refined to the smoothness of the other games as well.

Overall gameplay is pretty decent though you will get matched with player of a far higher player level leading to one sided matches. Tank levels are normalised, but player level(skill) is not.
